snippet.title: Refind Self: The Personality Test Game - Nintendo Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Analyze your personality by playing this simple exploration adventure game――
Refind Self: The Personality Test Game comes to Nintendo Switch this summer!

■Offical website: https://playism.com/en/game/refindself/
■Developer: Lizardry
■Publisher: PLAYISM
